      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. It drives beautifully and has plenty of life left for its next owner. If you're looking for a reliable, well-loved car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 32500.0,
