    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit features a broad power band with the double-VANOS system operating within factory tolerances. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring documented subframe reinforcement to manage the torque loads of the variable M differential. Shifting is handled by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox with a firm clutch take-up. While the vehicle exhibits minor cosmetic imperfections reflective of regular use, the suspension kinematics and braking system remain sharp, offering the balanced handling and high-RPM thrills characteristic of this platform.",
